# Next.js web

- Use App Router under `apps/web/`.
- Run **only in Docker** (`web` service); public entry is Nginx **8080**. Do not rely on host `pnpm dev` for the local stack.
- Auth: Next Route Handlers under `/api/auth/*` as BFF; JWT in httpOnly cookie (`marketplace_access_token`). Call Identity via `INTERNAL_API_URL` → gateway. See [docs/WEB_AUTH.md](docs/WEB_AUTH.md).
- UI: Tailwind CSS + shadcn-style components, `next-themes` (class / dark), forms with react-hook-form + zod.
- Prefer Server Components for catalog/product pages; client components for interactive cart/auth.
- i18n: **next-intl**, URL segment `[locale]` (`tr` default, `en` fallback). BFF sends `Accept-Language` matching locale ([docs/I18N.md](docs/I18N.md)).
- Route groups: public storefront (SEO), seller panel, admin — separate layouts when added.
